//---------------------------------HELP----------------------------

commands:
cd <directory>      Will change the shell from the current directory to the new directory. If Directory is not                         present, the shell will change the environment to "HOME"

clr                 Will clear the screen

dir <directory>     Will list the contents of the current directory.

environ             Will list all the environment strings.

echo <comment>      Will display <comment> followed by a new line.

help                Will display manual on how to use the shell

pause               Will pause the shell until enter is pressed

quit                Will quit the shell
